        "translations": {
          "en.tashayyu": [
            "25 – ʿĪsā b. al-Mustafād, al-Bajalī, Abū Mūsā al-Ḍarīr.  Narrations of his from Mūsā b. Jaʿfar عليه السلام are mentioned for him.  He has a book “al-Waṣiyya” whose sanad is not established.  In himself he is weak."
          ]
        }
      }
